author: Alana Mastrangelo
title: WHO Director Touts Teaming with Lady Gaga to Fight Coronavirus
description: We're saved! Thanks to Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, director general for the World Health Organization (WHO), who bragged about a recent phone call he had with pop star Lady Gaga about what she can do to fight the Chinese coronavirus pandemic.
